谷歌下一代人工智能模型 Gemini 性能优于 GPT-4 https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/06/google-next-gen-ai-model-gemini-outperforms-gpt-4/ https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/06/google-next-gen-ai-model-gemini-outperforms-gpt-4/#respondRyan Daws Wed, 06 Dec 2023 15:41:29 +0000 ApplicationsArtificial IntelligenceChatbotsCompaniesDevelopmentEnterpriseGoogleMachine Learningaiartificial intelligencebarddeepmindgeminigemini nanogemini progemini ultragoogle geminiModelmultimodal https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/?p=14016 <p>谷歌推出了 Gemini，这是该公司迄今为止功能最强大、用途最广泛的尖端人工智能模型。谷歌 DeepMind 首席执行官兼联合创始人 Demis Hassabis 介绍 Gemini 是一种多模态模型，能够无缝理解和组合各种类型的信息，包括文本、代码、音频、图像和视频。双子座出现<a class="excerpt-read-more" href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/06/google-next-gen-ai-model-gemini-outperforms-gpt-4/" title="ReadGoogle 的下一代 AI 模型 Gemini 性能优于 GPT-4">...阅读更多 ”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/06/google-next-gen-ai-model-gemini-outperforms-gpt-4/">Google 的下一代 AI 模型 Gemini 优于 GPT-4 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">AI News</a>上。</p> ; 
<p>谷歌推出了<a href="https://blog.google/technology/ai/google-gemini-ai/">Gemini</a> ，这是一种尖端的人工智能模型，是该公司迄今为止功能最强大、用途最广泛的模型。</p><p>谷歌 DeepMind 首席执行官兼联合创始人 Demis Hassabis 介绍 Gemini 是一种多模态模型，能够无缝理解和组合各种类型的信息，包括文本、代码、音频、图像和视频。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe title="Gemini：谷歌最新、最强大的人工智能模型" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jV1vkHv4zq8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></figure><p> Gemini 提供三个优化版本：Ultra、Pro 和 Nano。 Ultra 模型拥有最先进的性能，在语言理解方面超越了人类专家，并在从编码到多模式基准测试等任务中展示了前所未有的能力。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="835" height="1024" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-835x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-14017" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-835x1024.jpg 835w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-245x300.jpg 245w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-768x941.jpg 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-1253x1536.jpg 1253w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-1671x2048.jpg 1671w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-163x200.jpg 163w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-232x285.jpg 232w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-204x250.jpg 204w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-82x100.jpg 82w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks-49x60.jpg 49w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-text-benchmarks.jpg 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 835px) 100vw, 835px" /></figure><p> Gemini 的与众不同之处在于其原生的多模态性，无需将不同模态的单独组件拼接在一起。这种突破性的方法通过 Google 团队的大规模协作进行了微调，使 Gemini 成为一种灵活高效的模型，能够在数据中心和移动设备上运行。</p><p> Gemini 的突出特点之一是其复杂的多模式推理，使其能够以极高的精度从海量数据集中提取见解。该模型的能力扩展到理解和生成流行编程语言的高质量代码。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="693" height="1024" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-693x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-14018" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-693x1024.jpg 693w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-203x300.jpg 203w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-768x1135.jpg 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-1039x1536.jpg 1039w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-1385x2048.jpg 1385w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-135x200.jpg 135w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-193x285.jpg 193w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-169x250.jpg 169w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-68x100.jpg 68w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-41x60.jpg 41w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/google-gemini-multimodal-benchmarks-scaled.jpg 1732w" sizes="(max-width: 693px) 100vw, 693px" /></figure><p>然而，随着谷歌进入人工智能新时代，责任和安全仍然至关重要。 Gemini 经过严格的安全评估，包括偏倚和毒性评估。谷歌正在积极与外部专家合作，以解决潜在的盲点并确保模型的道德部署。</p><p> Gemini 1.0 现已在各种 Google 产品（包括 Bard 聊天机器人）中推出，并计划集成到搜索、广告、Chrome 和 Duet AI 中。不过，在等待监管机构批准之前，巴德升级不会在欧洲发布。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" title="马克·罗伯 (Mark Rober) 带着巴德 (Bard) 和 Gemini Pro 进行试飞" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mHZSrtl4zX0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></figure><p>开发者和企业客户可以通过Google AI Studio或<a href="https://cloud.google.com/vertex-ai">Google Cloud Vertex AI</a>中的Gemini API访问Gemini Pro。 Android 开发人员还可以通过<a href="https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2023/12/a-new-foundation-for-ai-on-android.html">AICore</a>使用 Gemini Nano 进行构建，AICore 是 Android 14 中提供的一项新系统功能。</p><p> <em>（图片来源：<a href="https://about.google/">谷歌</a>）</em></p><p><strong>另请参阅：</strong> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/01/ai-big-data-expo-impact-decision-making-in-marketing/"><strong>人工智能与大数据博览会：人工智能对营销决策的影响</strong></a></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="728" height="90" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728